Even as DINOBOT was speaking TARANTULUS was frantically trying to
contact someone, "I have lost contact with Cybertron." he said. He
looked over at DINOBOT, "Since your . . . um . . . demise partial
communication has been restored to Cybertron, we've even had a few . .
shall we say, visitors arrive."

SKYSHADOW turned to TARANTULUS, "So while we have been here fighting
with the Maximals, you have been in contact with Cybertron and failed
to mention it?" His gun was also out, only it was directed at
TARANTULUS rather than ANTAGONY.

"What are you a bunch of simpletons?" ANTAGONY said, her own anger
rising. "The more things change the less you have to go home to. Any
spoils or secrets or resources that were left on Cybertron will be
gone."

ANTAGONY turned to DINOBOT, "You ever heard of causality loops or
temporal destabilizations?" She fairly hissed as she glanced at the
group of them. "If we don't close the openings that lead to other
temporal zones soon there will be no temporal zones to return to." She
looked back at Dinobot, "And all of the creations of that temporal
zone stand a chance of ceasing to exist."

(TAG)

- Preston
